Filename target: macos-gatekeeper.png
Referenced from: docs/faq.md  (### macOS 提示"无法验证开发者"怎么办？)

How to capture:
  1. Build a fresh dmg with `scripts/build-dmg.sh`, install Markon.app to /Applications.
  2. Double-click Markon.app — the "无法打开 'Markon'…" dialog will appear. Close it.
  3. Open System Settings → Privacy & Security, scroll to the bottom.
  4. The "Markon was blocked…" row with the [仍要打开 / Open Anyway] button will appear.
  5. Screenshot just that section (Cmd+Shift+4, then Space, click the panel) and save as macos-gatekeeper.png in this directory.
  6. Delete this .tbd file.

Recommended size: ~1200px wide, retina (2x) preferred.
